title: Yasiin Gaye - I Want You 'Til The Summertime
description:
Teaser video: youtu.be/2OKKx2MLnNg

Download full album here: soulmatesproject.bandcamp.com/album/yasi…e-side-one

COMING SOON: "Yasiin Gaye: The Return (Side Two)" -Follow me on Facebook/Twitter to find out when:

Facebook: www.facebook.com/amerigogazaway
Twitter: twitter.com/amerigo615

Amerigo Gazaway’s *Soul Mates* series continues the theme of his previous work in creating collaborations that never were. On the series’ latest installment, Amerigo unites Brooklyn rapper Yasiin Bey (Mos Def) and soul legend Marvin Gaye for a dream collaboration aptly titled “Yasiin Gaye”. Building the album's foundation from deconstructed samples of Gaye’s Motown classics, Gazaway re-purposes the instrumentation into new productions within a similar framework. Carefully weaving Bey’s tangled raps and Gaye’s soulful vocals over his new arrangements, the producer delivers a quality much closer to an authentic collaboration than a lukewarm "mashup" album.

title: Kupla - Alpha Waves ('Subarctic' out May 5)
description: Bio @Kuplasound is a London based Finnish electronic music producer with previous experience in composing for dance and hip-hop. He has worked with numerous rappers in Finland and has now started to make his fresh futurebeats known to international audience as well. In March 2014 he released a single through Cosmonostro division, @Marmorean Records together with prestigious Chinese bass music producer @HowieLee. And now Kupla's first solo release "Subarctic EP" is about to be launched as well! Kupla - Subarctic Release Date : 05/05/2014 Tracklist 01 Cobra 02 Taiga Ranger 03 Alpha Waves 04 Spring Rewind 05 Lunar About Subarctic is an imaginative journey into emotional, musical and subconscious worlds. The instrumental beats are heavily influenced by modern electronic hip-hop with a touch of old Finnish mythology and mystique. Field recordings of northern forests, processed voice samples, clicks, clatters and soothing keys are all accompanied with lush hip-hop bass beats that will make your body and mind vibrate. Credits All tracks produced, mixed & mastered by Kupla Words by Kupla Artwork by @9uillaume6onte Social Twitter Facebook SoundCloud
